data.description: Wonderful, single story home, 5 bed, 3 bath (plus bonus room - can be an office, playroom, or guest room) nestled in a newer and quiet neighborhood. Open floor plan features 9' ceiling, formal dining area, breakfast nook & spacious living room for the whole family to enjoy. The gourmet kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, contemporary light pendants & recessed lightings. Designer paint & plank flooring all throughout the house. Backyard features a covered & cemented patio. Frontyard & backyard are beautifully landscaped.        Bring your buyers with you ASAP so they don't miss out on this opportunity !!!
